ZH: 我今天碰到了老朋友在超市。
EN: I ran into an old friend at the supermarket today.

ZH: 昨天我碰到了一个很有趣的人。
EN: I met a very interesting person yesterday.

ZH: 我下班的路上碰到下大雨。
EN: I ran into heavy rain on my way home from work.

ZH: 突然碰到一个陌生人给我递了一本书。
EN: Suddenly a stranger approached me and handed me a book.

ZH: 我们在图书馆碰到了彼此。
EN: We bumped into each other at the library.

ZH: 那天我碰到了我小时候的玩伴。
EN: That day I encountered my childhood playmate.

ZH: 我去超市碰到了我的同事。
EN: I bumped into my colleague at the supermarket.

ZH: 他碰到了一个有趣的问题，正在努力解决。
EN: He encountered an interesting problem and is working hard to solve it.

ZH: 他刚刚碰到了一条困难的挑战。
EN: He just encountered a difficult challenge.

ZH: 在公园里，我碰到了一个玩猫的小女孩。
EN: In the park, I met a little girl playing with a cat.

ZH: 进门的时候，他碰到了一个特别认识的人。
EN: When he walked in, he encountered someone he knew.

ZH: 我们的车昨晚碰到了一个故障。
EN: Our car encountered a problem last night.

ZH: 刚刚在大街上他碰到了一位长时间未见的朋友。
EN: Just now, he met a long-lost friend on the street.

ZH: 小明碰到了一只受伤的小鸟，把它护送到兽医那里。
EN: Xiaoming ran into an injured bird and escorted it to the vet.

ZH: 他在外面吃饭时碰到了一个熟人。
EN: He bumped into an acquaintance while dining out.

ZH: 聚会上，我碰到了一位有着相同兴趣爱好的朋友。
EN: I met a friend with similar interests at the party.

ZH: 他在街上碰到了一个求助的老人，主动帮助他。
EN: He encountered an elderly person asking for help on the street, and offered assistance.

ZH: 昨晚在电影院，我碰到了我的偶像。
EN: Last night at the movie theater, I met my idol.

ZH: 在健身房，她碰到了一个体育教练，让她更专注锻炼。
EN: At the gym, she met a sports coach who helped her focus on exercising.

ZH: 我在超市碰到了一个正在找工作的学生，给了他一些建议。
EN: I met a student looking for a job at the supermarket, and gave him some advice.
